# Helpful note:
# This app uses FDC endpoints documented by USDA, including /foods/search and /food/{fdcId},
# both of which require an API key. USDA states FoodData Central data are in the public domain
# under CC0 and notes default API rate limits of 1,000 requests/hour/IP. ([fdc.nal.usda.gov](https://fdc.nal.usda.gov/api-guide?utm_source=chatgpt.com))

